context:
  kind: schema
  version: 1.0
  task: .toon v1 DSL contract
required_sections[4]{id,name,rule}:
  1,context,Must exist as top-level block
  2,context.kind,Must be one of setup|suite|case
  3,context.version,Must be 1.0
  4,typed-collections,Use collection[count]{fields}: with deterministic row counts
typed_collections[3]{id,name,required_for_kind}:
  1,commands,setup
  2,cases,suite
  3,steps,case
notes[3]: context values use key:value pairs,list can be inline or row-based,suite case refs must point to test_cases/*.toon
